Package hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.hw03

Class Collection

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.custom.collections.hw03.Collection
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayIndexedCollection

    public class Collection
extends java.lang.Object
    The class represents a general collection of objects. You can find out collection's size, clear it, find out if it contains a certain value as well as add and remove values from the collection etc.
    Author:
    Dorian Ivankovic
